---
title: Portobello Mozza Burgers with Crispy Shallots and Spinach Salad
description: Ooey-gooey and crispy at the same time, this is the ultimate veggie burger! Served with a grainy mustard mayo and tender spinach salad, it has all the fixins' for a quick and satisfying dinner!
